parameters: \nc<Little Demon>Ah... I see. Can't be helped then.

\nc<Saki>*sigh*... (I'm not quite sure what's going on... Is it all
over now?)

\nc<Little Demon>Thanks to you, I had a great time... Now it's my turn to
help the Demon Cult.

\nc<Demon Customer>Right? If we have the Demon Cult, we can enjoy this kind of
thing again next time, right?
\nc<Human Guest>Well, if it's what the Demon Cult says, I'll listen.
\nc<Little Demon>...Is there anything else I can help with?
\nc<Administrator>Not at the moment. Please feel free to leave now.
\nc<Little Demon>Understood. Loyalty to the Demon Cult...

\nc<Administrator>Wait a second. Did all these guys get the memory erasure
hypnosis? I feel like there was a slightly unusual hypnosis
request...

\nc<Saki>(Eh? What are they talking about now? Memory erasure? No
way...)
\nc<Administrator>Ahh, I don't know. There's no time.
